  "2119830": {
    "name": "MISERY核处逢生",
    "steam_appid": 2119830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/2f524bf806c452e944f85835a6a74755.avif?t=1772034385\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/609e019fe4c8a027a2604b1d8b779eb4.poster.avif?t=1772034385\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/609e019fe4c8a027a2604b1d8b779eb4.webm?t=1772034385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/609e019fe4c8a027a2604b1d8b779eb4.mp4?t=1772034385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你扮演的是受雇保护扎斯拉维共和国某个秘密研究所的佣兵。<br> 扎斯拉维隔离区科研研究所（SIRZEZ）在战争前建立，用于研究异常现象和神秘物品。随着时间的推移，这些物品引发了国际军事集团之间的冲突。双方都不愿看到这些东西落入敌人之手，最终导致了核战争。<br> 警报响起——核弹即将来袭！你只有 60 秒时间，带上能拿的东西冲向地堡。<br> 接下来，真正的生存开始了。每天你都要进入隔离区，前往程序生成的地点寻找资源：废弃的军事基地、研究站、放射性荒地，以及破败的城市。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/c9b73a4f8029b346fa0f6b66be794b3a.poster.avif?t=1772034385\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/c9b73a4f8029b346fa0f6b66be794b3a.webm?t=1772034385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/c9b73a4f8029b346fa0f6b66be794b3a.mp4?t=1772034385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隔离区充满了秘密和致命陷阱，而辐射只是威胁的一部分。<br> 你会遇到为了生存而不惜杀人的其他幸存者、行为怪异的突变生物，还有各种神秘的异常现象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/443e6620df25d51768251b6f79387025.poster.avif?t=1772034385\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/443e6620df25d51768251b6f79387025.webm?t=1772034385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/443e6620df25d51768251b6f79387025.mp4?t=1772034385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有人知道这些异常现象的来源或原理。有些能帮助你，有些则会撕裂你。异常区域常常藏有稀有而珍贵的物品——它们被扭曲并带有独特效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/e577e82435e1226b00489a1420c2a4df.poster.avif?t=1772034385\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/e577e82435e1226b00489a1420c2a4df.webm?t=1772034385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/e577e82435e1226b00489a1420c2a4df.mp4?t=1772034385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地堡是你新的家。<br> 一点点扩建它：安装发电机（柴油、太阳能，甚至小矮人驱动的）、建造工作台、种植食物、做饭，用你从外面带回来的东西装饰庇护所：一张桌子、一只抽屉柜、一张旧沙发，甚至一块温暖的地毯。别担心，原来的主人已经不需要它们了。<br> 每次出击回来后，你都可以在研究所地下室的酒吧放松一下：喝点酒，和其他幸存者聊聊天，把你找到的战利品和稀有物品卖给商人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/db74bb3d151146e1087b5c5308b14a2c.poster.avif?t=1772034385\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/db74bb3d151146e1087b5c5308b14a2c.webm?t=1772034385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119830/extras/db74bb3d151146e1087b5c5308b14a2c.mp4?t=1772034385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记住，时刻关注你的生命状态。<br> 在隔离区，人们很容易死于饥饿、口渴、辐射病，或者在精神崩溃后对队友下手。白天出门搜刮，天黑前回到地堡。<br> 还有最后一件事：这片区域会干扰你的心智。压力过大时，你会听到耳语、看到不存在的幻象，甚至感到有人在盯着你看。一旦精神崩溃，就算是地堡也救不了你，什么都救不了你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在 MISERY 中活下去并不容易。<br> 但能一起经历这一切，是最宝贵的事情。<br> 和朋友一起探索废墟，互相掩护，围坐在火边，喝着仅剩的饮料，把烟雾吐进冷雨中——在这样的时刻，你会再次感到自己还活着！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 俄语<strong>*</strong>, 法语<strong>*</strong>, 意大利语<strong>*</strong>, 德语<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 西班牙<strong>*</strong>, 日语<strong>*</strong>, 韩语<strong>*</strong>, 波兰语<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙<strong>*</strong>, 简体中文<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲<strong>*</strong>, 繁体中文<strong>*</strong>, 土耳其语<strong>*</strong>, 乌克兰语<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
